{"word":"κουρά","slug":"κουρά","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κουρά</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:κείρω'><el>κείρω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a shearing</i> or <i>cropping</i> of the hair, <i>tonsure</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>a lock cut off</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}